{"tid":342698,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【404之謎】新昌股東通過7.6億售觀塘總部","createTime":"2017-07-31T22:24:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T00:13:46.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3c488884116d4fb4759b7c6ca7da7940fbea9bd6","tid":342698,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T22:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170731/large/1501508494_d1f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170731%2Flarge%2F1501508494_d1f8.jpg&h=5bd0e666&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新昌（404）出現債務問題後，集團在四月公佈計劃出售九龍觀塘偉業街的總部，惟交易一直拖延至今。最終集團今早召開股東大會，獲股東通過7.6億元向鑽海投資出售位出售該物業，交易料於未來兩星期內完成。新昌自4月初停牌至今。<br />\n<br />\n早前，新昌屢傳拖欠債息，市場關於其流動性風險，其後新昌曾向有「殼后」之稱的金利豐證券負責人朱李月華出售新昌管理（2340），套現約3.4億元。然而資金未解新昌之圍，往後市場亦傳出鄭家純及旗下周大福企業或成新昌白武士。<br />\n<br />\n在去年九月，知名沽空機構匿名分析（Anonymous Analytics）發表報告狙擊新昌集團(00404)， 指新昌新主人，即公司非執董林卓延以集團作為個人的垃圾場，新昌先後向林卓延收購有問題或不具盈利能力的地產發展項目，導致新昌債務急升。<br />\n<br />\n去年公司傳出陷入財困後，多次表明會研究出售旗下資產，包括今日獲通過的新昌總部。今早，本報記者曾前往上述新昌中心，惟公司管理層未有會見傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57025705&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57025705%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170731&d=T7NO%2FNCtn2YvK8aGtJMaTUjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=8028bb18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57025705%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170731&h=6adbd558\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57025705&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170731</a>"},{"pid":"22895a4b181f78beec10b4f7083847002456793c","tid":342698,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T23:49:00.000Z","msg":"呢間野最好快啲執柒"},{"pid":"bd9597f0df16a225e02dc9de0d9f24fb5eb50cd5","tid":342698,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T23:52:33.000Z","msg":"呢間野仲繼續請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce5e5cd0a89cd49cfa859503b807bdeac478680","tid":342698,"uid":71725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T23:56:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9ea963ae34f97438cc2d438d59df42c6603f2e9","tid":342698,"uid":53866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:13:46.000Z","msg":"2萬6請ae添"}]}